dct_description_sm: "First exhibited before the National Association for the Promotion of Social Science; October, 1858." Removed from: Condition of Liverpool ... / by the Rev. A. Hume. Liverpool : T. Brakell, 1858 (1447.999 v. 76). Includes inset: Liverpool, showing the locality of pauperism, cholera & violent deaths.
